---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Contact Us - AI Tools HQ"
  description="Get in touch with AI Tools HQ. Suggest a tool, report an issue, or just say hello."
>
  <main class="contact-page">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>Contact Us</h1>
      <p>We'd love to hear from you</p>
    </header>

    <div class="contact-grid">
      <section class="contact-info">
        <div class="info-card">
          <h2>üìß Email</h2>
          <p>For general inquiries and tool suggestions:</p>
          <a href="mailto:hello@ai-tools-hq.com">hello@ai-tools-hq.com</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card">
          <h2>üîß Tool Suggestions</h2>
          <p>
            Know an AI tool we should review? We're always looking for great tools to add
            to our directory. Send us the name and website!
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card">
          <h2>üêõ Report Issues</h2>
          <p>
            Found outdated information or a broken link? Let us know and we'll fix it ASAP.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card">
          <h2>ü§ù Partnerships</h2>
          <p>
            Interested in partnering with AI Tools HQ? We're open to collaborations that
            benefit our readers.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="faq">
        <h2>Frequently Asked</h2>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How do you choose which tools to review?</h3>
          <p>
            We focus on tools that solve real problems and have proven user bases. We also
            take reader suggestions seriously.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Are your reviews sponsored?</h3>
          <p>
            No. Our reviews are independent. While we use affiliate links, they never
            influence our ratings or recommendations.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How often do you update reviews?</h3>
          <p>
            We aim to update reviews when tools have major changes. If you notice outdated
            info, please let us know.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can I request a specific comparison?</h3>
          <p>
            Absolutely! Email us with the tools you'd like compared and we'll consider it
            for a future article.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .contact-page {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .page-header p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .contact-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .info-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  .info-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .info-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .info-card a {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .info-card a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
  }

  .faq h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .faq-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .faq-item h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .faq-item p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .contact-page {
      padding: 7rem 1.5rem 3rem;
    }

    .contact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
